text: George Chesser (September 11, 1942 – November 12, 2008) was an American football running back and punter. He played for the Miami Dolphins from 1966 to 1967. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:2008 deaths Category:American football running backs Category:American football punters Category:Ole Miss Rebels football players Category:Delta State Statesmen football players Category:Miami Dolphins players
